Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.43,0:22:56.37,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur5}那鲜红的感性如此美丽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.93,0:23:01.61,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur5}刺穿了模糊的正义
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.61,0:23:05.15,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur5}自作自受的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.15,0:23:07.07,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur5}与命运纠缠融合
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.07,0:23:09.21,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur5\3c&HC7842C&}call me distortion
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.21,0:23:11.94,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur5\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\3a&H6F&}请别记恨我
